{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":760,"text":"I started Improv Everywhere\nabout 10 years ago"},{"time":2960,"text":"when I moved to New York City\nwith an interest in acting and comedy."},{"time":6480,"text":"Because I was new to the city,\nI didn't have access to a stage,"},{"time":9480,"text":"so I decided to create\nmy own in public places."}]},{"cues":[{"time":12880,"text":"So the first project\nwe're going to take a look at"},{"time":15280,"text":"is the very first No Pants Subway Ride."},{"time":17200,"text":"Now, this took place in January of 2002."},{"time":19200,"text":"And this woman is the star of the video."},{"time":21160,"text":"She doesn't know she's being filmed."},{"time":22920,"text":"She's being filmed with a hidden camera."},{"time":24880,"text":"This is on the 6 train in New York City."},{"time":26840,"text":"And this is the first stop along the line."},{"time":28960,"text":"These are two Danish guys"},{"time":30240,"text":"who come in and sit down\nnext to the hidden camera."},{"time":33880,"text":"And that's me right there in a brown coat."},{"time":35920,"text":"It's about 30 degrees outside."},{"time":37600,"text":"I'm wearing a hat. I'm wearing a scarf."},{"time":40160,"text":"And the girl's going\nto notice me right here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":44880,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":50280,"text":"And as you'll see now,\nI'm not wearing pants."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52520,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":56640,"text":"At this point --"},{"time":58600,"text":"at this point she's noticed me,"},{"time":60120,"text":"but in New York there's weirdos\non any given train car."},{"time":62760,"text":"One person's not that unusual."},{"time":64239,"text":"She goes back to reading her book,\nwhich is unfortunately titled \"Rape.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":67680,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":71040,"text":"So she's noticed the unusual thing,\nbut she's gone back to her normal life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":74600,"text":"Now, in the meantime, I have six friends"},{"time":76560,"text":"who are waiting\nat the next six consecutive stops"},{"time":78920,"text":"in their underwear as well."},{"time":80600,"text":"They're going to be entering\nthis car one by one."},{"time":82960,"text":"We'll act as though\nwe don't know each other."},{"time":85480,"text":"And we'll act as if it's just\nan unfortunate mistake we've made,"},{"time":88520,"text":"forgetting our pants\non this cold January day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90720,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":105800,"text":"(Laughter continues)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":117280,"text":"So at this point,"},{"time":118560,"text":"she decides to put the rape book away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120920,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":123000,"text":"And she decides to be a little bit\nmore aware of her surroundings."},{"time":126360,"text":"In the meantime, the two Danish guys\nto the left of the camera,"},{"time":129360,"text":"they're cracking up."},{"time":130600,"text":"They think this is the funniest thing\nthey've ever seen before."},{"time":133600,"text":"And watch her make eye contact\nwith them right about now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":138440,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":143280,"text":"And I love that moment in this video,"},{"time":145120,"text":"because before it became\na shared experience,"},{"time":147720,"text":"it was something\nthat was maybe a little bit scary,"},{"time":150520,"text":"or something that was\nat least confusing to her."},{"time":152800,"text":"And then, once it became\na shared experience,"},{"time":154920,"text":"it was funny and something\nthat she could laugh at."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157360,"text":"So the train is now pulling\ninto the third stop along the 6 line."}]},{"cues":[{"time":174720,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":178200,"text":"So the video won't show everything."},{"time":179920,"text":"This goes on for another four stops."},{"time":182040,"text":"A total of seven guys\nenter anonymously in their underwear."},{"time":185320,"text":"At the eighth stop,\na girl came in with a giant duffel bag"},{"time":188080,"text":"and announced she had\npants for sale for a dollar --"},{"time":190560,"text":"like you might sell batteries\nor candy on the train."},{"time":193800,"text":"We all very matter-of-factly\nbought a pair of pants, put them on"},{"time":196880,"text":"and said, \"Thank you.\nThat's exactly what I needed today,\""},{"time":199640,"text":"and then exited without\nrevealing what had happened"},{"time":202840,"text":"and went in all different directions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":204680,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":207680,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":209720,"text":"So that's a still from the video there."},{"time":212440,"text":"And I love that girl's reaction so much."},{"time":214440,"text":"And watching that videotape later that day"},{"time":216464,"text":"inspired me to keep doing what I do."},{"time":218800,"text":"And really one of the points\nof Improv Everywhere"},{"time":221360,"text":"is to cause a scene in a public place"},{"time":223400,"text":"that is a positive experience\nfor other people."},{"time":225640,"text":"It's a prank, but it's a prank\nthat gives somebody a great story to tell."},{"time":229120,"text":"And her reaction inspired me"},{"time":230520,"text":"to do a second annual\nNo Pants Subway Ride."},{"time":232560,"text":"And we've continued to do it every year."},{"time":234489,"text":"This January, we did\nthe 10th annual No Pants Subway Ride"},{"time":237200,"text":"where a diverse group of 3,500 people"},{"time":239560,"text":"rode the train in their\nunderwear in New York --"},{"time":241840,"text":"almost every single\ntrain line in the city."},{"time":243920,"text":"And also in 50 other cities\naround the world,"},{"time":246320,"text":"people participated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":247560,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":249720,"text":"As I started taking improv class\nat the Upright Citizens Brigade Theater"},{"time":253160,"text":"and meeting other creative people\nand other performers and comedians,"},{"time":256440,"text":"I started amassing\na mailing list of people"},{"time":258519,"text":"who wanted to do these types of projects."},{"time":260519,"text":"So I could do more large-scale projects."},{"time":262480,"text":"Well, one day I was walking\nthrough Union Square,"},{"time":264840,"text":"and I saw this building,\nwhich had just been built in 2005."},{"time":268400,"text":"There was a girl in one of the windows\nand she was dancing."},{"time":271240,"text":"It was very peculiar,\nbecause it was dark out,"},{"time":273440,"text":"but she was backlit\nwith florescent lighting."},{"time":275680,"text":"She was very much onstage"},{"time":276960,"text":"and I couldn't figure out\nwhy she was doing it."},{"time":279200,"text":"After about 15 seconds,\nher friend appeared --"},{"time":281400,"text":"she had been hiding behind a display."},{"time":283240,"text":"They laughed, hugged\neach other and ran away."},{"time":285400,"text":"Maybe she had been dared to do this."},{"time":287160,"text":"So I got inspired by that."},{"time":288480,"text":"Looking at the entire facade --\nthere were 70 total windows --"},{"time":291440,"text":"and I knew what I had to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":292840,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":294400,"text":"So this project is called Look Up More."},{"time":296320,"text":"We had 70 actors dress in black."},{"time":297920,"text":"This was completely unauthorized."},{"time":299560,"text":"We didn't let the stores know\nwe were coming."},{"time":301720,"text":"And I stood in the park giving signals."},{"time":303640,"text":"The first signal was for everybody\nto hold up these four-foot tall letters"},{"time":307160,"text":"that spelled out \"Look Up More,\""},{"time":308760,"text":"the name of the project."},{"time":311200,"text":"The second signal was for everybody\nto do jumping jacks together."},{"time":315400,"text":"You'll see that start right here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":317040,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":319520,"text":"And then we had dancing.\nWe had everyone dance."},{"time":321760,"text":"And then we had dance solos"},{"time":323120,"text":"where only one person would dance\nand everybody would point to them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":326360,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":333120,"text":"So then I gave a new hand signal,"},{"time":334760,"text":"which signaled the next soloist\ndown below in Forever 21,"},{"time":338160,"text":"and he danced."},{"time":340280,"text":"There were several other activities."},{"time":342080,"text":"We had people jumping up and down,\npeople dropping to the ground."},{"time":345520,"text":"And I was standing\njust anonymously in a sweatshirt,"},{"time":348000,"text":"putting my hand on and off of a trashcan\nto signal the advancement."},{"time":351280,"text":"And because it was in Union Square Park,\nright by a subway station,"},{"time":354480,"text":"there were hundreds of people by the end\nwho stopped and looked up"},{"time":357640,"text":"and watched what we were doing."},{"time":361640,"text":"There's a better photo of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":363200,"text":"So that particular event\nwas inspired by a moment"},{"time":367000,"text":"that I happened to stumble upon."},{"time":369360,"text":"The next project I want to show"},{"time":370880,"text":"was given to me\nin an email from a stranger."},{"time":373720,"text":"A high school kid in Texas\nwrote me in 2006"},{"time":376080,"text":"and said, \"You should get\nas many people as possible"},{"time":378560,"text":"to put on blue polo shirts and khaki pants"},{"time":381160,"text":"and go into a Best Buy and stand around.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":383440,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":385880,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":388160,"text":"So I wrote this high school kid\nback immediately"},{"time":392680,"text":"and I said, \"Yes, you are correct."},{"time":394360,"text":"I think I'll try to do that\nthis weekend. Thank you.\""},{"time":396880,"text":"So here's the video."}]},{"cues":[{"time":398280,"text":"So again, this is 2005."},{"time":399800,"text":"This is the Best Buy in New York City."},{"time":402320,"text":"We had about 80 people\nshow up to participate,"},{"time":405120,"text":"entering one by one."},{"time":406440,"text":"There was an eight-year-old girl,\na 10-year-old girl."},{"time":408941,"text":"There was also a 65-year-old man\nwho participated."},{"time":412000,"text":"So a very diverse group of people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":414000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":415160,"text":"And I told people,\n\"Don't work. Don't actually do work."},{"time":417840,"text":"But also, don't shop."},{"time":419080,"text":"Just stand around\nand don't face products.\""},{"time":421520,"text":"Now you can see the regular employees"},{"time":423360,"text":"by the ones that have\nthe yellow tags on their shirt."},{"time":425880,"text":"Everybody else is one of our actors."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427640,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":429520,"text":"The lower-level employees\nthought it was very funny."},{"time":432000,"text":"Several of them went\nto go get their camera from the break room"},{"time":435000,"text":"and took photos with us."},{"time":436280,"text":"A lot of them made jokes\nabout trying to get us to go to the back"},{"time":439360,"text":"to get heavy television sets\nfor customers."},{"time":442000,"text":"The managers and the security guards,\non the other hand,"},{"time":444960,"text":"did not find it particularly funny."},{"time":447280,"text":"You can see them in this footage."},{"time":448920,"text":"They're wearing either\na yellow shirt or a black shirt."},{"time":451560,"text":"And we were there probably 10 minutes"},{"time":453400,"text":"before the managers decided to dial 911."}]},{"cues":[{"time":455920,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":458200,"text":"So they started running around"},{"time":460000,"text":"telling everybody the cops were coming,\n\"Watch out, the cops are coming.\""},{"time":463600,"text":"And you can see the cops\nin this footage right here."},{"time":466240,"text":"That's a cop wearing black right there,\nbeing filmed with a hidden camera."},{"time":469760,"text":"Ultimately, the police\nhad to inform Best Buy management"},{"time":472440,"text":"that it was not, in fact, illegal\nto wear a blue polo shirt and khaki pants."}]},{"cues":[{"time":476040,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":478360,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":481880,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":483120,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":484840,"text":"So we had been there for 20 minutes;\nwe were happy to exit the store."},{"time":489280,"text":"One thing the managers were trying to do\nwas to track down our cameras."},{"time":493360,"text":"And they caught a couple of my guys\nwho had hidden cameras in duffel bags."},{"time":496880,"text":"But the one camera guy they never caught"},{"time":498809,"text":"was the guy that went in\njust with a blank tape"},{"time":501040,"text":"and went over to the Best Buy\ncamera department"},{"time":503280,"text":"and just put his tape\nin one of their cameras"},{"time":505440,"text":"and pretended to shop."},{"time":507520,"text":"So I like that concept of using\ntheir own technology against them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":510680,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":512400,"text":"I think our best projects\nare ones that are site-specific"},{"time":515120,"text":"and happen at a particular\nplace for a reason."},{"time":517320,"text":"And one morning, I was riding the subway."},{"time":519297,"text":"I had to make a transfer\nat the 53rd St. stop"},{"time":521440,"text":"where there are\nthese two giant escalators."},{"time":523480,"text":"And it's a very depressing place\nto be in the morning, it's very crowded."},{"time":526960,"text":"So I decided to try and stage something"},{"time":528880,"text":"that could make it as happy\nas possible for one morning."},{"time":532400,"text":"So this was in the winter of 2009 --\n8:30 in the morning."},{"time":535920,"text":"It's morning rush hour."},{"time":537480,"text":"It's very cold outside."},{"time":539240,"text":"People are coming in from Queens,"},{"time":540880,"text":"transferring from the E train\nto the 6 train."},{"time":543800,"text":"And they're going up\nthese giant escalators"},{"time":546920,"text":"on their way to their jobs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":550840,"text":"[Rob wants]"},{"time":556235,"text":"[to give you]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":560175,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":561349,"text":"[a high five!]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":562626,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":565094,"text":"[Get ready!]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":566367,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":573360,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":580000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":581240,"text":"So there's a photograph\nthat illustrates it a little bit better."},{"time":584280,"text":"He gave 2,000 high fives that day,"},{"time":586960,"text":"and he washed his hands\nbefore and afterward"},{"time":589360,"text":"and did not get sick."},{"time":590800,"text":"And that was done also without permission,"},{"time":592824,"text":"although no one seemed to care."}]},{"cues":[{"time":594960,"text":"So I'd say over the years,"},{"time":596280,"text":"one of the most common criticisms\nI see of Improv Everywhere"},{"time":599520,"text":"left anonymously on YouTube comments"},{"time":601440,"text":"is: \"These people\nhave too much time on their hands.\""},{"time":604600,"text":"And you know, not everybody's\ngoing to like everything you do,"},{"time":607560,"text":"and I've certainly developed a thick skin\nthanks to Internet comments,"},{"time":610880,"text":"but that one's always bothered me,"},{"time":612560,"text":"because we don't have\ntoo much time on our hands."},{"time":614920,"text":"The participants\nin Improv Everywhere events"},{"time":617040,"text":"have just as much leisure time\nas any other New Yorkers,"},{"time":619720,"text":"they just occasionally choose\nto spend it in an unusual way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":622640,"text":"You know, every Saturday and Sunday,"},{"time":624400,"text":"hundreds of thousands of people each fall"},{"time":626480,"text":"gather in football stadiums\nto watch games."},{"time":629200,"text":"And I've never seen anybody comment,\nlooking at a football game,"},{"time":632280,"text":"\"All those people in the stands,\nthey have too much time on their hands.\""},{"time":635760,"text":"And of course they don't."},{"time":637040,"text":"It's a perfectly wonderful way\nto spent a weekend afternoon,"},{"time":639920,"text":"watching a football game in a stadium."},{"time":641800,"text":"But I think it's also\na perfectly valid way"},{"time":644000,"text":"to spend an afternoon\nfreezing in place with 200 people"},{"time":647200,"text":"in the Grand Central terminal"},{"time":648880,"text":"or dressing up like a ghostbuster"},{"time":651200,"text":"and running through\nthe New York Public Library."}]},{"cues":[{"time":653480,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":655600,"text":"Or listening to the same MP3\nas 3,000 other people"},{"time":658840,"text":"and dancing silently in a park,"},{"time":661000,"text":"or bursting into song in a grocery store"},{"time":663200,"text":"as part of a spontaneous musical,"},{"time":665440,"text":"or diving into the ocean in Coney Island\nwearing formal attire."}]},{"cues":[{"time":668880,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":670320,"text":"You know, as kids, we're taught to play."},{"time":672280,"text":"And we're never given a reason\nwhy we should play."},{"time":674680,"text":"It's just acceptable\nthat play is a good thing."},{"time":676920,"text":"And I think that's sort of\nthe point of Improv Everywhere."},{"time":679680,"text":"It's that there is no point\nand that there doesn't have to be a point."},{"time":683000,"text":"We don't need a reason.\nAs long as it's fun"},{"time":685040,"text":"and it seems like\nit's going to be a funny idea"},{"time":687280,"text":"and it seems like the people\nwho witness it"},{"time":689600,"text":"will also have a fun time,"},{"time":691080,"text":"then that's enough for us."},{"time":692480,"text":"And I think, as adults, we need to learn"},{"time":694520,"text":"that there's no right\nor wrong way to play."}]},{"cues":[{"time":697000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":698240,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}